                    The Ambassador in France (
                        Caffery
                    ) to the Acting Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945Berlinv01</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d555</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">555</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-07-10T12:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-07-10T12:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc>            <textClass>
